<ITEM><LIST>
<HEAD>&s;ons of <HI>Sir THEOBALD, 6 &amp; 7</HI> years old.</HEAD>
<ITEM><HI>WILIBALD,</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>OTTOMAR,</HI></ITEM>
</LIST></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>BERTRAM,</HI> an old boor.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>CYRILLUS,</HI> an abbot of the Premon&s;trantes.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>MISTIVOI,</HI> chief of the Heathen tribe.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>A MONK.</HI></ITEM>
